Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, the oneness of the evolution then, up through the animal kingdom, up through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of the 200s, up through that which doesn't have within it enough energy, it has
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to go out and eat others because it lacks energy, not because it's wicked or because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's bad, because it doesn't have within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, as we sacrifice our personal lives for the welfare of others, as we in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,do so for the sake of the world, then by that intention do we sanctify the world, sanctify
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by our intention that human life becomes sanctified, all that's personified in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,life of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The message radiates out 2,000 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So as we support that energy now, then we are serving life right this moment, right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are, all of us, collectively serving the welfare of all of human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us see if that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact, O Lord Jesus, that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask, what can I do, do me a favor, don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop doing things, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be the fulfillment of the potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fulfillment of the potentiality which you have karmically inherited, or you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would never be in a room like this, because a room like this is full of people destined
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone that is in this room is destined for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a fact, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, why else would you be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would you be here, if this was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People destined to become tennis players are at a class on tennis this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,People destined to become enlightened are in a class on being enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here then has to own that within themself that you all innately have elected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,by your own free will to be that which upholds all of life in its expression in its humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by your very being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This very moment we are upholding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a part of that 15% that's upholding the other 85% just by the virtue of our commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to truth, to learn about truth, to my sharing with you what I've learned about truth and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what I hope will be useful to the world and in today's world, its application to world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,peace and bringing about peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How to express that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That intelligence, how to express that intelligence in our international diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So spirituality is just not a Sunday morning thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world that by its sheer intention tends to bring forth truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and integrity in others because non-integrity when it's confronted by integrity tends to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,cringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It pulls back from the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So just being what you are tends to suppress non-integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Being what you are radiates out an energy field and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective consciousness of mankind keeps evolving and it's going to continue further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw on that curve how it's going like this and how it's going like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of mankind is rapidly moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So this group here is in the forefront of that graph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right there where it's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about as far as consciousness has evolved up to this point which you're hearing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness has evolved any further than this point in a way that can be communicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way that can be communicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain information is transformational.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It has within itself a transformational power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we share with you information which in and of itself, in and of itself with no effort
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put in no effort at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To just be with the information is already transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereby, your life becomes a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become a blessing to the world by the nature of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so prayerfully, we'll stop for the day for the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a little longer time for questions and answers later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll take a break, and then we'll do questions and answers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to fulfill what is being unanswered in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very Christian, so I'm very Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so our collective intention is impacting the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it. It's ringing. It's shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're going to do Nico's chant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we're going to have the questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to change microphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have not been here before are not aware that Nico does the Lotus Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chant it in Sanskrit. It's magical. Calibrates over 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico chanting the Lotus Sutra in Sanskrit is a rare opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've all earned through karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic merit. Take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The last of you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to start the questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The great people with questions on this side of the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the people with just one book signed on that side of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This question I wrote down because I wanted to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've been thinking about it for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a question about karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have written that choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That choice supersedes karma, and that at a consciousness level...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't supersede. It determines it. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And that at a consciousness level of 600 or higher, you transcend personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, is it possible, say after going through the course of miracles or something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose not to be subject to karma below the level of 600?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be choosing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the ego persists...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it, the karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 600, it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is all that exists, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As a contribution to the good and welfare...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants a hug now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just wonderful being here in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this one she speaks into?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this one doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the satellite room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the satellite room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And this was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about non-resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine and I have had some really good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,following your idea of if you have an acute injury
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that you let go of the resistance to the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It works really, really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm wanting to ask you is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you take that to some chronic type of illness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,like ringing of the ears or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing applies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because that intensifies your focus and concentration on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which tends to magnify the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the field in which it's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens is it becomes forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you recall it, you'll re-experience it, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll find that most things,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't pay attention to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not within the focus of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though they're still there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I focus, you know, on the site of the amputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the pain of it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because the pain of it never really physically disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as the source of suffering, it disappears
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin by ignoring it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and letting go of wanting to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And also there's certain karmic undoingness going on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered if that might not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've recalled in front of this group
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or similar groups, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,very specific recall of exactly what the karmic indebtedness was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that accounted for the excruciating experience
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I went through at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember extremely well what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So if that's the case, if it's a karmic undoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then we should just go with that karmic undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's also a way of non-resisting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of letting go of the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be a way of intellectually contextualizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't know what this serves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but for thee, O Lord, do I accept it and surrender to thy will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And just go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For however long it goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's your karmic undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard you say that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to disappear something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,accept it totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you go ahead and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,well, this is karmic undoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you focus on becoming one with the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and focus on the higher spiritual qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the first thing you do is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop labeling it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,indigestion, asthma, or whatever you're calling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't give it any name,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're not experiencing asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not experiencing arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is let go of calling it anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're only left with sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, if you let go of resisting a local pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,stop calling it pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that it's only sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you let go of trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that your mind is localizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you constantly let go of resisting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the sensation will become general.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell it's gone into your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the pain or the nausea or whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're letting go of resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes general instead of specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just keep surrendering to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and it becomes like diffuse in your whole aura
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than localized to your ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do that as a process.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And just continue to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like being born ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what can you do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could resist and resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but that wouldn't be very wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other techniques you'd like to share with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we were in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We were on a radio program with a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who's called sort of a local shock jock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really enjoyed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a crew of three or four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very well-known program in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Man for a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Man cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, man cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he carries on a conversation with callers in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fast mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a big kick out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But one of his crew standing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we all have to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One of his crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, is just plain stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just am stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he'll say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And by God, it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it is really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just breaks up everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this stupid guy just accepts that he's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't battle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he probably makes more than you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of us put together, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being stupid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He just says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he says really dumb things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I want a hamburger or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like, in the middle of a question like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, I want a hamburger, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dumb thing to say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when a person's asking you a question, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, so totally accepting that you're stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and ugly can be very beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what you, what you accept about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what am I supposed to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what you accept about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody can hit you there, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensitive people are people who have not accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,their downside, and they're defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they're vulnerable all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you accept, if you sit down, I advise the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,sit down and list every single possible defect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have or could be perceived as having,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and let, and it's okay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's okay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what could be said to you that would upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've completely disarmed the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,by accepting your downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:21:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're short and skinny,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're never gonna make the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not tall enough to make the swimming team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too frail to be out there on the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You just ain't never gonna be an athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just never been very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Four eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One time we were, after, after,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been four eyes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After A Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,after A Course in Miracles meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Lower East Side in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous Jewish restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner goes on for about three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They stagger out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the corner is this bag lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And here are these black plastic bags
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,full of New York City garbage sitting on the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this, right out of a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,bag lady is poking around through these things, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all stand around and ask for a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all bless her and send her her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, her head comes out of these pile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of black plastic bags, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And she looks at me and she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you looking at, four eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A hug. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, maybe you can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't knock the flowers over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get Sharon Raine to go to the bookstore, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon Raine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are all these here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I sign them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, glad somebody keeps track of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this one, all beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:24:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is unconditional love a realistic intention for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,An average American?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is unconditional love a realistic intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't it be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.16,0:24:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is let go of your reservations about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,judgmentalism and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, unconditional love is a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.02,0:24:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is, you know, love at 500 is between a this and a that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a me and a you, you and your cat, you and your dog, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.35,0:24:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540, it becomes a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the way you are in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lovingness towards all of life and all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.69,0:24:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and a sense of humor about everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:24:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and also the capacity to see the beauty of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a way of being, therefore, it's not something that requires effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.66,0:25:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to try to be unconditionally loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You just become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers are glad to see you arrive, because you're not going to pick them unnecessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.63,0:25:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You revere all the beauty and all its innate incredible perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.98,0:25:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be careful, because you won't be able to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.44,0:25:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's just if you let the energy of the beauty radiate for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.98,0:25:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then the questions and answers come to a stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.16,0:25:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because you become one with that field, because beauty is innate to divinity, you know, except
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:25:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:26:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.68,0:26:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.68,0:26:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.68,0:26:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I possibly have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug if you don't knock the flowers over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.01,0:26:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.01,0:26:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, would you comment on the relationship between love and passion?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.86,0:26:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.00,0:26:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between consciousness and schizophrenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.80,0:26:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not really related.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.80,0:26:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not really related.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.78,0:26:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is an overall nonlinear field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Schizophrenia is a disorganization of content, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.73,0:27:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The linear content follows certain laws, and when it gets fractured, we call it schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.33,0:27:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Schizophrenia is the loss of the capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.61,0:27:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't differentiate between the categories, as described by Immanuel Kant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.93,0:27:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various levels of abstraction, and when you confuse the material with the intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.40,0:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when you lose the differentiation of levels of abstraction, then you're no longer following
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.60,0:27:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the order of logic, subject and predicate and verb, you know, and therefore you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.66,0:27:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,constrained by...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.66,0:27:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by integrity, by the integrity of logic, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you fall below 400, you're no longer logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.68,0:27:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.58,0:28:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.64,0:28:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, you've commented before on the level of consciousness of humanity at
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.26,0:28:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the time of birth of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.26,0:28:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And also the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.26,0:28:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.26,0:28:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Krishna and the Bhagavad Gita, that whole Indian history?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.40,0:28:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you comment on that particular period?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.32,0:28:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.86,0:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Bhagavad Gita calibrates 900 or over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Aryan sages, you see, 7 to 10,000 B.C., the pre-Indian culture, the Aryan, already
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.63,0:28:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,birthed great spiritual genius, 900, 950 was the great sages, and out of the great sages
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.62,0:28:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,arose the Gitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.84,0:28:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.84,0:28:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ancient Hindu teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.98,0:28:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was already old, already old.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.72,0:29:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual enlightenment was already known, you know, prior to the birth of Buddha or
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't reach this side of the world because there was no communication with this side
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.63,0:29:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.63,0:29:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was completely isolated from this side of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.21,0:29:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was like reborn in the form of Jesus Christ, reborn in Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.78,0:29:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of the birth of Buddha, the consciousness level of mankind was...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.38,0:29:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.38,0:29:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of the birth of Jesus Christ, it was at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.83,0:29:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And how about like at the time of Krishna?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.47,0:29:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.47,0:29:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the great Aryan sages of 7 to 10,000 B.C. had already experienced the enlightened condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.57,0:29:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And their writings are still way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:29:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.36,0:29:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.36,0:29:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.36,0:30:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when I read what Krishna said in the Bhagavad Gita, that's exactly the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.09,0:30:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who worship me by whatever name are dear to me, and I will take them unto myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.17,0:30:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.17,0:30:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.17,0:30:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.80,0:30:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about art.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.80,0:30:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.42,0:30:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what Michelangelo calibrated at, but would his art that came through him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.42,0:30:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to calibrate higher than...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.42,0:30:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.25,0:30:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, the production is that of the radiance of the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:31:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Writers, the writings of spiritual teachers usually calibrate about just exactly what
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.05,0:31:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the teacher's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.05,0:31:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me what you calibrate at then, without saying it, by what your books
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.59,0:31:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate at.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.59,0:31:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About Michelangelo, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.59,0:31:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.59,0:31:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.59,0:31:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.59,0:31:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an artist, and that's why I was asking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.59,0:31:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it just clicked like, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.59,0:31:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Michelangelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.59,0:31:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.59,0:31:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrated really high.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.59,0:31:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.59,0:31:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated Michelangelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.59,0:31:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, he's way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.59,0:31:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.59,0:31:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.59,0:31:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.59,0:31:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss you, Midna.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.59,0:31:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.59,0:31:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they personalize, they personalize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.59,0:31:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.43,0:31:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence, then, you learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.23,0:31:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.23,0:31:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.23,0:31:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.23,0:31:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.23,0:31:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence then utilizes the machinery, which is this body and this languaging and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.35,0:31:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.35,0:31:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence utilizes the machinery to express itself in a form comprehensible to the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.55,0:32:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.38,0:32:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.38,0:32:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.64,0:32:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking today about non-doing and non-effort, which is exactly opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.64,0:32:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,how I'm living my life, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.64,0:32:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-doing and non-effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.64,0:32:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-doing and non-effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.64,0:32:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an interstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be busy as all get out on the outer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.64,0:32:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.64,0:32:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.64,0:32:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it actually brings me to confronting a paradigm that I struggle with, which is,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.74,0:32:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible for mankind to live on this planet without having to work, having to do
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.74,0:32:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the paradigm that we see out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.74,0:32:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's certainly been my fantasy to live on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.74,0:32:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to just be, and not have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.74,0:32:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're a spirit, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.74,0:32:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought, well, maybe it's a certain consciousness level.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.74,0:32:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get to be a certain consciousness level, then can you truly just trust that the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,will provide everything for you, including the money, including the house, where you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.83,0:32:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to work a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.83,0:32:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.83,0:32:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.83,0:32:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.83,0:32:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.83,0:33:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.83,0:33:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.83,0:33:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.83,0:33:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.83,0:33:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.83,0:33:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.83,0:33:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.83,0:33:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.83,0:33:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.83,0:33:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.83,0:33:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.83,0:33:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.83,0:33:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.83,0:33:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.50,0:33:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to find a job in a spiritual community or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.02,0:33:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop resisting hunger, you don't have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.50,0:33:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When your material motivation disappears, there has to be some other motivation, or
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you come to a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.20,0:33:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.52,0:33:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You come to a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.25,0:33:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the world can worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.05,0:33:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you topple over, you topple over, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.07,0:34:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like the spin of all that we have to do in this life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.65,0:34:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is so distracting, and it's driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.65,0:34:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Distracting from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what I want to just be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.99,0:34:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what you are already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.97,0:34:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.99,0:34:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a losing conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.73,0:34:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not mankind's birthright to trust in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and a very radical trust I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.22,0:34:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.02,0:34:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not talking about the physical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.50,0:34:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking physical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.94,0:34:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the physical realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.86,0:34:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was in radical trust, I mean really radical trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.38,0:34:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,like I know the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.02,0:34:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.17,0:34:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.00,0:34:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.87,0:34:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.07,0:34:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't have to try to create my physical self.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.39,0:34:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.05,0:34:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're willing to sacrifice it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.15,0:34:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,something will come along,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.35,0:35:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will propagate the activity of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.59,0:35:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.71,0:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.94,0:35:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it to be irrelevant, but still make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.84,0:35:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.32,0:35:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you eat or not is the world's worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, can I ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.35,0:35:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.15,0:35:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I suffer kind of from a deep love of astrology.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.99,0:35:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You suffer from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.27,0:35:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A deep love of astrology.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.75,0:35:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A deep love of astrology.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.83,0:35:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought a deep bad case of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.81,0:35:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.49,0:35:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,loved astrology for lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.09,0:35:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.83,0:35:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.49,0:35:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the way they...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.97,0:35:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're stuck with the stars, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.43,0:35:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.37,0:35:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the way they've guided me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.15,0:35:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.71,0:35:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how come you got...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.21,0:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have any questions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.87,0:35:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I read your books,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.25,0:35:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it put the seed of doubt, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.67,0:36:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about the astral realms within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.11,0:36:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm having difficulty...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.97,0:36:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have difficulty making the break
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.40,0:36:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,between that paradigm
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.82,0:36:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and, I guess, just releasing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.02,0:36:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That astrology dominates your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.04,0:36:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrological influences?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.16,0:36:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.08,0:36:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Saturn's going over your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.06,0:36:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,right, when Saturn is having lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.45,0:36:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I feel like I give away my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.17,0:36:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the same time, I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.51,0:36:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're giving away your power
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.83,0:36:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to the immaterial, to the non-material,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.19,0:36:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.91,0:36:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical has no intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.19,0:36:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how a whirling dirt ball
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.87,0:36:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,can have intention about your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.03,0:36:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.12,0:36:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.38,0:36:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dirt ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.60,0:36:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.50,0:36:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.22,0:37:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.02,0:37:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.11,0:37:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.63,0:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The physicality of a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.29,0:37:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,has consciousness to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.08,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're projecting its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.04,0:37:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The only power it has
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.90,0:37:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you project to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.04,0:37:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you believe that this star
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.58,0:37:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,or this constellation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.66,0:37:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,does what it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.32,0:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens if you disconnect
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.92,0:37:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your belief from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's just a whirling dirt ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.90,0:37:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you put your faith in God?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.57,0:37:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.99,0:37:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the material, physical universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.48,0:37:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving it the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.58,0:37:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all, of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We lectured about it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.89,0:37:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no this that can cause a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your intention
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.21,0:37:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that a this should align with a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.59,0:37:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness of mankind evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.71,0:37:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time of the harmonic concordance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.04,0:38:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which is all enveloping,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.04,0:38:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,including the physical universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.26,0:38:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is all in accord with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.26,0:38:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in accord with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.64,0:38:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's all part of the one whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.58,0:38:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the likelihood of something here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.72,0:38:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,happening in conformity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.60,0:38:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with this being here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.68,0:38:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is because they're both coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.62,0:38:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the same oneness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.60,0:38:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of this is causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.74,0:38:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're separating it into a duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.84,0:38:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe is a unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.32,0:38:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So there would be the concordance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.18,0:38:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is perhaps favorable
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.00,0:38:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.38,0:38:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.36,0:38:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not because this is causing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.20,0:38:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.32,0:38:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only mistake you're making is causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still likely a concordance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.60,0:38:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if for no other reason
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.05,0:38:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,than the power you give it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.25,0:38:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your own belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.95,0:38:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So to exit a paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.52,0:38:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,do you just exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:39:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.20,0:39:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm recontextualizing it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.60,0:39:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That the universe is part of the oneness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.98,0:39:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of the will of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.48,0:39:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's beyond causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.36,0:39:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.06,0:39:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I look at a hologram, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.42,0:39:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I look at a hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.82,0:39:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as I walk around the hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.80,0:39:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks, what does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.04,0:39:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I photograph it and speed it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like there's a this causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no this causing any that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.35,0:39:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's moved
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.23,0:39:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is my point of observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.82,0:39:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't make any difference
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.30,0:39:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's these flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.12,0:39:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or an infinite world of plants
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.88,0:39:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or a planet swirling about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.30,0:39:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the same holographic phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.06,0:39:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,see, in which everything is part of the whole, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.75,0:39:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're trying to separate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.43,0:39:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this part of the hologram
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.75,0:39:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,from this part of the hologram
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.03,0:40:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and saying this is cause and this is effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.37,0:40:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can switch it around and say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.23,0:40:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.07,0:40:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is turn time backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Jesus teach that you get to heaven through astrology?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.96,0:40:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.43,0:40:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.70,0:40:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Buddha teach that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.70,0:40:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.70,0:40:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Krishna teach that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.70,0:40:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.70,0:40:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who taught it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.34,0:40:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Some divine being?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.81,0:40:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.81,0:40:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what she's saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.42,0:40:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll get caught up in an interest
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and put a lot of time and energy into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't have a vested interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.42,0:40:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that it's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.90,0:40:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just that it's not contextualized correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.90,0:40:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of the overall whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.48,0:41:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.36,0:41:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On a lighter note,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.36,0:41:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a present for your cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.36,0:41:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were calibrating cats
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.36,0:41:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for cat food last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is what I feed my cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.36,0:41:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't think you've ever heard
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.36,0:41:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of this particular cat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.36,0:41:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.36,0:41:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You might like to calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.36,0:41:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called dead mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.71,0:41:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A bag of dead mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.71,0:41:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.71,0:41:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.71,0:41:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.71,0:41:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.71,0:41:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.29,0:41:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.29,0:41:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this cat food calibrates over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.29,0:41:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.29,0:41:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My cat has good karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.29,0:41:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you bless food,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.29,0:41:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it jumps in calibration 10 to 15 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.29,0:41:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you love your pet,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.29,0:41:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do is you feed your kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.29,0:41:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or your doggy or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.29,0:41:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you bless this food
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.29,0:41:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of thy love, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.29,0:41:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because the dog's wagging tail is 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.29,0:42:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitty's purr is 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.29,0:42:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're just thanking God for their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.29,0:42:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.29,0:42:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You bless their food,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.29,0:42:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.29,0:42:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the level of the kitty food jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.61,0:42:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was getting some pretty high numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on this food,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.61,0:42:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you said that most...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.61,0:42:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's over 200, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.61,0:42:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Most cat food, you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.61,0:42:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't calibrate much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.61,0:42:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.61,0:42:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some big-selling brands
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,whose names I don't want to mention
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.61,0:42:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's litiginous world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.61,0:42:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.61,0:42:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know my cat pointed it out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.61,0:42:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because she wouldn't eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.61,0:42:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or you wouldn't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.61,0:42:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping to get a hug as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.61,0:42:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a dollar on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.61,0:42:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.61,0:42:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.61,0:42:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give me kitty food?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.61,0:42:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.61,0:42:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's around the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.61,0:42:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.61,0:42:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.61,0:42:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the kitty food, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.61,0:42:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the kitty food.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.61,0:42:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know she'll love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.61,0:42:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.61,0:42:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.61,0:42:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.61,0:42:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me thank you for the kitty food.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.61,0:42:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.74,0:42:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you, my kitty food.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.74,0:42:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.74,0:42:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We all thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.74,0:42:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the great kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.74,0:42:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the great kitty,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.74,0:42:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we do thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.90,0:42:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.90,0:43:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you for a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.90,0:43:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kick it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they want freebies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.90,0:43:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.90,0:43:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This mic is working okay, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.90,0:43:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.90,0:43:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.90,0:43:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.90,0:43:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.12,0:43:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into astrology, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.12,0:43:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.73,0:43:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I once caught Venus in my backyard, dude, and you know what was Saturn, by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.73,0:43:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I reported it to the police, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.14,0:43:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
