Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.09,0:43:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.09,0:43:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.09,0:43:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.09,0:43:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.09,0:43:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.09,0:43:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.10,0:43:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.10,0:43:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.10,0:43:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.10,0:43:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.10,0:43:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.10,0:43:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.10,0:43:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.19,0:43:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.19,0:43:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have a question I didn't have before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.15,0:43:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.11,0:43:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first read your book, at the end, about the author, I wept, and the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.30,0:44:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,being that you were talking about the energy flows that you had from your body, which I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.26,0:44:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have experienced from mine at times, and it just brought tears to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.70,0:44:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.80,0:44:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See, when we spoke, we didn't use that term today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.68,0:44:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that's an omission of my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.04,0:44:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because over 200, what happens is the kundalini energy begins to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.16,0:44:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it had a better name.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.70,0:44:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual energy, spiritual energy begins to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.59,0:44:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what shifts you over to the processing a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the kundalini energy that actualizes the formation of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.83,0:44:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain is a consequence of the kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.19,0:44:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So an animal does not have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.33,0:44:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Although maybe cats and dogs do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.77,0:44:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.83,0:44:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had experiences where I felt it come all the way through my body, out my arm, out my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.99,0:45:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And one time I was sitting across from a lady and my hand was on her thigh and I went into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.09,0:45:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I lifted my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.29,0:45:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She actually levitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.53,0:45:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I grumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.83,0:45:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to a parapsychology department at a university after that happened to ask them what possibly had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.18,0:45:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And all they said to me, well, we heard of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.66,0:45:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at it as a love-giving experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.36,0:45:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.74,0:45:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me what they were doing was just copying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.46,0:45:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.80,0:45:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy, we didn't talk about that today, results in the so-called SIDDHAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.88,0:45:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-I-D-D-H-A-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.52,0:45:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Paranormal Phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.52,0:45:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance viewing, clairaudience, clairvoyance, psychometry, you could grab this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.38,0:45:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who owned it, where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.78,0:45:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw all of it's been spoken in the front of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.14,0:45:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All those things are spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.96,0:46:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to heal things, heal sicknesses, heal beings, the miraculous, all that is a consequence of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.77,0:46:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It does it of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.38,0:46:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.58,0:46:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it does it of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.20,0:46:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.42,0:46:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go next door and heal some crippled lady and she'll get up and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.66,0:46:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big surprise, you know, it's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.34,0:46:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Second question, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.40,0:46:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it does all those things of its own, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.00,0:46:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.93,0:46:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock on my microphone, you'll hear from my lawyer right into my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.46,0:46:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I can't talk that way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.34,0:46:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a perpetrator and I'm a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.34,0:46:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.28,0:46:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.12,0:46:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.74,0:46:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.10,0:46:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the gift that you are to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.98,0:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, would you help me recontextualize the lower astral, the luciferic, the satanic?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.26,0:47:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the energies of the negative energies over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.12,0:47:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer, you see, the luciferic is like about 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.18,0:47:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.34,0:47:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's secular.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.14,0:47:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants to take God out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.96,0:47:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.42,0:47:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Lucifer did not want to acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.16,0:47:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The sovereignty of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.20,0:47:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, therefore, it's a competition for power and prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.05,0:47:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the luciferic that came to me as I went through the final pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.83,0:47:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The luciferic came to me as a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.56,0:47:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you realize that you're beyond all answerability or consequence, beyond all karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.25,0:47:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all power is yours, own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.47,0:47:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.49,0:47:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a temptation then, which comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.95,0:48:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the luciferic has to do with pride and power, prestige, and it distorts reason and logic via the distortions of the hermeneutics of relativistic epistemology.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.09,0:48:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where it invades the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.15,0:48:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds very comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, the professorships of the universities have gone down, down, down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.75,0:48:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The professors of six of the world's, United States greatest universities calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.45,0:48:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of the professors calibrate higher than the student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.53,0:48:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the sacrificing of truth, you know, for relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.50,0:48:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the problem with relativism?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.22,0:48:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It denies the reality of the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.16,0:48:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Mad Hatter's Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, a thing only means what I mean it to mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.68,0:49:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That denies, you see, the reality of the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.08,0:49:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that I'm God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.60,0:49:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How I see it and how I define it is how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.64,0:49:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then, therefore, you can ridicule science and reason and logic and ethics and tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.36,0:49:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.13,0:49:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All morality and ethics are then hated constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.38,0:49:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Against freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.42,0:49:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.42,0:49:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom of the id.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud's id.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.42,0:49:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which seeks no accountability, answerability, or responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.90,0:49:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we see a society in which responsibility is now projected onto some supposedly evil external cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.12,0:50:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Making the Marxian dialectic error even more severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.62,0:50:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.62,0:50:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.62,0:50:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.03,0:50:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see a downgrading of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.03,0:50:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it means that the way I see it is superior to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.10,0:50:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that my way of seeing it is superior to all the greatest minds that have ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.48,0:50:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that I am really superior to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.57,0:50:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great game to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.07,0:50:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.07,0:50:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.07,0:50:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.39,0:50:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Satanic is represented by...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.49,0:50:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Torture, pain, and dynamiting busloads of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.49,0:50:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to find some way of finding humor in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.61,0:51:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to find humor in 300 kids being blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.28,0:51:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the humor is in the absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.97,0:51:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.97,0:51:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're blowing up all these innocent children for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.97,0:51:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.06,0:51:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's really more the ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.06,0:51:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More the absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.22,0:51:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would be sad if it weren't so destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.18,0:51:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.44,0:51:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the enemy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.44,0:51:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy right now is that energy field which comes out of Wahhabism.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.44,0:51:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahhabism.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.46,0:51:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The tradition that I grew up in, and I'll be brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.66,0:51:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.66,0:51:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.17,0:51:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that the astral, the Satanic was so demonized, to put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.17,0:51:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that people were afraid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.17,0:51:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we call it demonic, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.17,0:52:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.17,0:52:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.17,0:52:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If the energies get low enough, we call them demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.17,0:52:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.17,0:52:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, because they become homicidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.17,0:52:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.38,0:52:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.38,0:52:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower astral realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.38,0:52:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.38,0:52:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dollar for a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.38,0:52:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.38,0:52:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.38,0:52:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.61,0:52:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many domains, many realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.86,0:52:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.86,0:52:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get into heaven today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.24,0:52:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.95,0:52:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just say it to make sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.95,0:52:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.95,0:52:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl could not have said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.47,0:52:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop breathing, you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.47,0:52:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.47,0:52:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I got to come back again to teach you what I didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.17,0:52:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.17,0:52:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.23,0:52:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't just one heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.23,0:52:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a whole celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.23,0:52:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Many religions are the sole pipeline to that region of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.23,0:53:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they claim exclusivity to heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.71,0:53:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they are exclusive to that portion of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.71,0:53:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is that neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.71,0:53:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you got to have 30 wives in order to get into heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.90,0:53:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,their hunk of heaven, that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.90,0:53:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,People only have one wife, you don't get admitted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.51,0:53:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are multiple heavens suitable for each set of belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.77,0:53:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.44,0:53:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget Krishna said,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.44,0:53:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all who are devoted to me are dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.44,0:53:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you think God is in a pumpkin and you worship the pumpkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.44,0:53:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.44,0:53:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to pumpkin heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.44,0:53:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.52,0:53:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so inspired when I hear you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.52,0:53:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wish I could just be your apostle or something
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow you around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.52,0:53:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is about the negative emotional states
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.52,0:53:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,below consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.52,0:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.52,0:54:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard those referred to as illusory or non-real or even non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.52,0:54:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're based on misperception, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.52,0:54:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem justified because that's how you're perceiving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.52,0:54:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, you're perceiving it that way
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.52,0:54:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's what your level of consciousness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.52,0:54:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So the two reinforce each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.52,0:54:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they're non-existent,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.52,0:54:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how can they still have an energy associated with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.52,0:54:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because perception determines what has no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.87,0:54:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those levels have energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.87,0:54:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one has a justified level and energy, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.87,0:54:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have energy, then how can like imagination or something have energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.51,0:54:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's illusory, it's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.51,0:54:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like fear is not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.51,0:54:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not real in what sense depends on what you mean by real.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.51,0:54:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Real with a small R, real with a big R.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.34,0:54:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's real with a big R in which none of this applies.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.38,0:54:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why when you're over 600, nothing, test goes weak anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.38,0:54:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.38,0:55:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're above consciousness level 600, you don't go weak anymore with kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.38,0:55:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing makes you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.76,0:55:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So those negative emotional states,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.76,0:55:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that they are fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.76,0:55:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.76,0:55:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize they are perception, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.76,0:55:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But that perception creates its own reality within its own energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.76,0:55:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is hatred and it does have its own energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.11,0:55:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see that the basis of the hatred is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.40,0:55:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We gave you a way out of hatred today forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.40,0:55:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates, when he said that every man chooses only the good,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.66,0:55:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,right away you got, oh, that's the tool, the understanding I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.66,0:55:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can forgive everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.66,0:55:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They choose only the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.07,0:55:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They blow up a whole lot of children because that to them is the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.07,0:55:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.07,0:55:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.07,0:55:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.07,0:55:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm signing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.07,0:55:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quarter after four.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.07,0:55:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many people are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.07,0:55:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.07,0:55:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.07,0:55:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.07,0:55:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.07,0:56:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.07,0:56:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,God's problem, not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.07,0:56:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't run this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.07,0:56:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't run this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.97,0:56:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.97,0:56:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.97,0:56:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm glad you reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.97,0:56:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.97,0:56:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.97,0:56:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you mentioned that there are a number of mantras that calibrate in the 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.00,0:56:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's also my understanding that for the past 2,000, 3,000 years and up until today,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.00,0:56:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that the majority of enlightened beings have come from the Eastern religions, primarily Buddhism,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.00,0:56:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which seems to have a predominant practice of using mantras.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.00,0:56:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not due to the mantras.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.03,0:56:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mantra is an expression of the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.03,0:56:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason Buddhism is so effective is because it looks for divinity within.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.74,0:56:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in the Western world, God is pictured and held by belief systems to be transcendent,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.96,0:57:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,out there, somewhere ahead in time or behind in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.96,0:57:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Created the universe, disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.96,0:57:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're going to meet the big man over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.57,0:57:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.57,0:57:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So God is pictured as transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.63,0:57:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Eastern understanding, Hindu and Aryan, East Indian and Buddhic, the God is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.75,0:57:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is the imminent God within as the Self, with a capital S, as the source of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.39,0:57:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which one experiences in the divine state is the unmanifest becoming manifest as your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.39,0:57:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of joy is the awareness of the source of your existence, which is ever-present.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.39,0:57:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say thee, O Lord, I'm speaking to that which is already present,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.95,0:58:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,not something in the future or something in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.40,0:58:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.71,0:58:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was discovered when you let go of the barriers, when you let go of duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.74,0:58:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality shines forth as self-realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.74,0:58:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It does so spontaneously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.25,0:58:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you caused it, but because when the clouds are removed, the sun shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.44,0:58:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't cause the sun to shine forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.44,0:58:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I just wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.55,0:58:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a question, but I first wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.55,0:58:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one that, and Lou and Shelly helped me out of this call group.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.55,0:58:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you gave me some suggestions last time I spoke to join an Al-Anon group, which I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.55,0:58:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.55,0:58:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And things are moving along.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.55,0:58:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm learning to let go and let God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.55,0:58:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And just feeling the flow of God just working through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.55,0:58:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You took my advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.55,0:59:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.55,0:59:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am going to leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.58,0:59:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has it. Few people take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.58,0:59:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I get $20 in?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.58,0:59:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you get a dollar for taking my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.65,0:59:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my question is, it deals with undoing karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.65,0:59:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you mentioned, you talked about it briefly in another question.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.65,0:59:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides becoming the field and maybe surrendering our will to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.74,0:59:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is there specific things, like if we would ask, God, is there karma that I can get rid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.74,0:59:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what could I do to precipitate that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.74,0:59:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does it just come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.74,0:59:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it shows up of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.74,0:59:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.74,0:59:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hustle it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.74,1:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although spiritual work often results in your life becoming chaotic for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.06,1:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because spiritual work then begins removing the karmic layers and you move rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.06,1:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.61,1:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people think their life is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.02,1:00:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.02,1:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that they're moving it ahead faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.02,1:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.02,1:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And people go into beatific states and then it doesn't last.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.06,1:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And they feel very sad about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.06,1:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they've transcended their karma for up to now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.06,1:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next layer of what needs to be undone becomes undone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.06,1:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the flashes of beauty and inner light are presaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.12,1:00:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They tell you that you're in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.12,1:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.12,1:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.12,1:00:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you undo that next bunch of negative karma, it comes back again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.12,1:00:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's recurrent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.12,1:00:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.12,1:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.12,1:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.12,1:01:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.46,1:01:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who takes my advice deserves a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.73,1:01:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.14,1:01:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.14,1:01:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question about this old book that I found.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.14,1:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called The Life and Teachings of the Great Masters of the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.14,1:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a famous book.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.14,1:01:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering, my question was, have you ever read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.14,1:01:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Handle or calibrate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.14,1:01:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.14,1:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very familiar with it, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.14,1:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.72,1:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.72,1:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.72,1:01:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.72,1:01:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.72,1:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I had.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.61,1:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.61,1:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The book calibrates over 500 verses.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.61,1:01:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,550, 560, 580, 575, 560, 565, 560.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.61,1:01:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I raise the 560?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.61,1:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.61,1:01:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.61,1:01:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the wonderful enlightenment that you've given us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.61,1:01:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.70,1:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.70,1:01:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.80,1:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.80,1:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.80,1:01:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.80,1:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.80,1:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.44,1:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.44,1:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.44,1:01:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.44,1:01:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.44,1:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.44,1:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.44,1:01:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.44,1:01:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.44,1:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I got a hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.44,1:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time, my first exposure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.44,1:02:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, arm?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.44,1:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.44,1:02:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my first exposure to yourي
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.76,1:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.76,1:02:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.86,1:02:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.86,1:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,300, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.86,1:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've recovered, though, you've recovered from it pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.86,1:02:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.86,1:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me the Bill O'Reilly of spirituality, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.86,1:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,my husband and I and soon after we had him we realized that there were things
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.24,1:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that were not just right with him so when he started school we were having
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.14,1:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,problems and eventually he's now 37 he has been diagnosed as bipolar borderline
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.72,1:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have stuck by him and we will continue to do that but I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.58,1:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if there was it's been very draining on us and yet we don't want to abandon what
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.52,1:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we started I mean we were told by a pediatrician way in the beginning that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.86,1:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we could probably give him up because he was suspecting something might be wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.70,1:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with him because of his biological mother yes and we decided that we would
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.28,1:03:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,not do that so that was our decision to keep him and we bonded and of course I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.70,1:03:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,bonded with him within five minutes when they gave him to me
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.98,1:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you're welcome
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.58,1:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're still suffering he's 37 he's he finally left the United States he's
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.87,1:03:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,living in New Zealand now but still very very dependent on us because he's never
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.05,1:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,been able to work he's very brilliant but he doesn't have any judgmental with
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.07,1:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,him to control his or to regulate his daily activities and he's chronically
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.83,1:03:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,disabled yes yeah so I was wondering I mean I know that was kind of a far-out
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.61,1:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,question but
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.33,1:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything that can be done on a miraculous or a spiritual level I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.95,1:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we've tried my husband and I you know we've we've done a lot of reading we've
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.63,1:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,done a lot of growing in the last 37 years well you then you'd let go on to change him no we
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.33,1:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want to change him we can't all right so what is the problem the problem
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.63,1:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is how do we I mean we've gotten to the point where we are so exhausted now you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.81,1:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,must be resisting that otherwise you're not exhausted you're exhausted from what
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.33,1:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.33,1:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.33,1:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.32,1:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.32,1:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.32,1:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.32,1:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.32,1:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.32,1:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.32,1:04:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.32,1:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.61,1:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.61,1:04:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.61,1:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.61,1:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.61,1:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.61,1:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.94,1:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.94,1:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.94,1:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.94,1:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.22,1:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.22,1:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.93,1:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.93,1:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.93,1:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.93,1:04:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.93,1:04:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.93,1:04:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.93,1:05:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.97,1:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.97,1:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To accept what is, then let go, wind it, change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.51,1:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the prayer you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.31,1:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't. We realize that there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.15,1:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's an intellectual. You haven't accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.81,1:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance, it's neither this nor that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.69,1:05:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.10,1:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My kitty is orange.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.16,1:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just accept it's orange.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.66,1:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make it black. I don't want to make it gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.04,1:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't grieve the fact that it's orange.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.14,1:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just let it be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.54,1:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you let your son be what it is, like a kitty cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.85,1:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't give me any buts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.65,1:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.75,1:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the first step in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.61,1:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.91,1:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.86,1:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the first step in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.36,1:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all step groups have that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.44,1:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First step, you admit that your power was sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.34,1:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.71,1:06:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The context for my question is that I have
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.51,1:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual healing practice where I work with people
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.55,1:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.77,1:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience or become aware of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.23,1:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And on a few occasions, it seems that I have helped someone
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.01,1:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who is more spiritually advanced than myself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.53,1:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to higher levels than they've ever attained before.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.49,1:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet there's a traditional belief that a master can't take a student
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.62,1:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond his own level.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.96,1:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you're a master?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.04,1:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but is it possible for me or for anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.24,1:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to help someone go beyond their own level?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.08,1:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.80,1:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give a person a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.92,1:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And they become enlightened as a result of applying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.08,1:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're only a stepping stone, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.18,1:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.10,1:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intention of the other person, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.96,1:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of the other person
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.66,1:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,will activate a single sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.68,1:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you needed was that one sentence to shoot through.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.37,1:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's their intention that activates that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.41,1:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.31,1:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.81,1:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a facilitator.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.55,1:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.06,1:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry the message, but not the person.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.92,1:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.92,1:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.92,1:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.92,1:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You give them the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.92,1:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.92,1:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One morning they wake up and they say, oh, Zowie.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.92,1:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man chooses only the good.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.92,1:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.92,1:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.92,1:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that today, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.92,1:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.92,1:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates told me that a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.92,1:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.92,1:07:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm working with them, I'm praying that they receive a healing and a teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.92,1:07:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And they often later come back and say, you know, after I left, it occurred to me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.92,1:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think, okay, that's the teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.92,1:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know it didn't come through me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.92,1:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.92,1:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you put in your ore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.92,1:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.92,1:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all you can do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.92,1:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.92,1:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to the other person and their acceptance and their karma, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.92,1:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.92,1:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.92,1:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.92,1:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.10,1:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.10,1:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about your.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.10,1:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a comment earlier this year in one of your videos that I saw about your orange
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.10,1:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.10,1:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was the only one in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.10,1:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.32,1:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, is there just one human being in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.31,1:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's there over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.31,1:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200, you have individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.31,1:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.31,1:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have responsibility for your choices and your actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.31,1:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animal kingdom has one central consciousness that radiates out in multiple bodies so that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.40,1:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you meet one orange kitty, you've met them all in a way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.24,1:08:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.24,1:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.24,1:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.24,1:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.24,1:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.24,1:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You got an orange kitty in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.24,1:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You got kitty food?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.24,1:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.24,1:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.24,1:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.24,1:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm making big money today.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.24,1:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, Dr. Hawkins, is would eating raw food benefit the body and nervous system
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.52,1:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Kundalini energy to come up through?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.52,1:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it prepare it better?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.52,1:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.45,1:09:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If eating raw food would prepare the body…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.45,1:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.45,1:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.45,1:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it has anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.45,1:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.45,1:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.55,1:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.55,1:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's non-linear, non-physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.55,1:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a non-linear, non-physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.55,1:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I don't think physical manipulations have any influence on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.55,1:09:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On whether the energy comes up easily or…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.55,1:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.55,1:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,…whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.55,1:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.55,1:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when it's ready to come up, it comes up by itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.55,1:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.55,1:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's not ready, you know, I don't believe in trying to promote it artificially,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.68,1:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because then it's not real, it's not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.68,1:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.71,1:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.71,1:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about automatically.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.71,1:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As you become more loving towards all of life and all of the expressions, then it begins
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.71,1:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to flow automatically of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.71,1:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.71,1:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.79,1:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.79,1:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.79,1:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.79,1:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you so much for answering that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.79,1:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.79,1:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.79,1:10:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to have a hug, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.79,1:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.79,1:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.91,1:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.91,1:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be out of here at 5 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.91,1:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Half hour, we've got…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.61,1:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.61,1:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.61,1:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.61,1:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my mother, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.61,1:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.61,1:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.61,1:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.61,1:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.71,1:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys always calibrate the group consciousness before and after?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.96,1:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you done that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.96,1:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.96,1:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually do it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.96,1:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.96,1:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.96,1:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.96,1:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be interested in doing that today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.96,1:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see what the consciousness level of the audience did today.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.96,1:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.96,1:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.96,1:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the group here, the consciousness level of the group, from the beginning to the end
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.96,1:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lecture, it went up over 8 points, 9 points, 10 points, 11 points, about 10, 11
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.73,1:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,points.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.73,1:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.73,1:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.73,1:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It just occurred to me on the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.73,1:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.73,1:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's because…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.37,1:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's got another question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.40,1:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent a dollar already.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.40,1:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.85,1:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.85,1:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.85,1:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is studying someone who has quit eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.85,1:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been a student of that subject for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.85,1:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What subject?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.85,1:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some people call it breatharianism, but there are people that are spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.85,1:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,not eating in China.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.85,1:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, breatharians.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.85,1:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.85,1:11:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And they give them a whole different label, and they don't even know the term.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.85,1:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm wondering, you know, because a lot of these people that are doing this happen
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.85,1:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to be spiritual-oriented.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.85,1:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there's a connection between the two, but here's my question, because I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.85,1:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to pull together some material on the subject of health, and I'm going to make
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.85,1:12:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a brief mention of breatharianism.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.85,1:12:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to know whether you have to have a certain calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.85,1:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.85,1:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not necessarily connecting it with spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.85,1:12:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.85,1:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like, based on paying attention to your research, that it has to be at least
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.85,1:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,200.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.85,1:12:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.11,1:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't too many breatharians around.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.11,1:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like I said, NASA's got one, and they're studying them for the obvious reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.24,1:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible for you to find out if...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.24,1:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired of eating?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.24,1:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.24,1:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop eating any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.24,1:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.24,1:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.24,1:12:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.24,1:12:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.65,1:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.78,1:12:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a calibrated level of consciousness that you have to reach?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.78,1:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I never calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.78,1:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.78,1:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I never did research it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.78,1:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.78,1:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we asked about one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.78,1:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hold in mind something.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.91,1:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'm holding in mind is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.91,1:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a genuine one in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.91,1:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only one I know about.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.91,1:13:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.91,1:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.91,1:13:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it possible to ask if there's a calibrated level of consciousness in order to...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.91,1:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.91,1:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to research it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.91,1:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.91,1:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be too much time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.91,1:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more than one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.91,1:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.91,1:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And could you see whether this book is integrous or not just by the Kinesian?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.91,1:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.91,1:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.91,1:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.91,1:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.91,1:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.91,1:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.35,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.35,1:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.35,1:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.35,1:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you transcend the body quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.35,1:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.35,1:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.35,1:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.35,1:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.35,1:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.35,1:13:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.35,1:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.35,1:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.35,1:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.35,1:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.65,1:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.65,1:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.65,1:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.65,1:13:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.68,1:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.68,1:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.68,1:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.68,1:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with Thomas Hora that wrote Beyond a Dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.68,1:14:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.68,1:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was learning to...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.68,1:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of authors I'm not familiar with are multitudinous.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.68,1:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.68,1:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.88,1:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.88,1:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas Hora?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.88,1:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond a Dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.88,1:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.88,1:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.88,1:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Joel Goldsmith?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.88,1:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We only calibrated people that calibrated 460 and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.88,1:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.88,1:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.88,1:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.88,1:14:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.88,1:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.88,1:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.88,1:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.88,1:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.36,1:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.36,1:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.36,1:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.36,1:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.36,1:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.36,1:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.36,1:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Joel Goldsmith was over 460, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.36,1:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-five, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.36,1:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was, still.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.36,1:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.36,1:14:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only other thing I'd mention is, on a personal level, it seems like...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.36,1:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm getting old or silly or what, but, I tear up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.48,1:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear up?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.48,1:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.48,1:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.48,1:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.48,1:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.48,1:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a symptom of me becoming more spiritual, or just a silly old lady?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.22,1:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.22,1:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.22,1:14:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, we'd have to research it individually.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.22,1:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You tear up with what? Joy or sadness?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.26,1:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, anything that moves me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.76,1:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, that's just, that's very common.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.58,1:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do spiritual work, you find yourself crying all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.98,1:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.84,1:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain level in which the slightest sign of love or tenderness or something, you just weep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.88,1:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you go through it, it's sort of tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.16,1:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in an airport waiting for a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.00,1:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see this wife look at her husband, and you can just see the love.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.38,1:15:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just break out in tears about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.32,1:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, that's comforting because my grown children just tease me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.76,1:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, are you going to cry now?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.92,1:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In monasteries, it's, you know, well-known.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.32,1:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And people often cry for several years.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They hit a certain level of love, and they cry sometimes for a couple years.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.46,1:15:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.48,1:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cry for a couple years.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.09,1:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Invest in Kleenex and be with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.05,1:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, at least we're not going in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.32,1:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, beauty makes you weep, beautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.24,1:16:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The most common experience of it is beautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.90,1:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you hear the introduction to Lohengrin or Tannhäuser.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.80,1:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you hear the music mount, Jesus, God, it just wipes you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.42,1:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, anything of great beauty just wipes you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.67,1:16:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So be prepared to be wiped out pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.82,1:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or avoid the beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.32,1:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that everything in the world considers ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.64,1:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it's innate beauty, so you can't escape it either.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.01,1:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you know, that's the phase you go through.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.30,1:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.44,1:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.42,1:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.28,1:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't cry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.58,1:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.78,1:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.08,1:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful state you're in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.50,1:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.36,1:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.16,1:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you the time of sitting down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.60,1:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.30,1:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.76,1:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.14,1:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oggins, thank you very much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.32,1:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to ask you if you might illustrate the kinesthological method for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.10,1:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't see it today?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.40,1:17:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you do it with her, but I don't know how to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.94,1:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.94,1:17:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to have a partner the way I do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.44,1:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a way of doing it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.44,1:17:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.44,1:17:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.44,1:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that reliable.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.44,1:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.63,1:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try it with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.63,1:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.84,1:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because nothing makes me go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.86,1:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.86,1:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't tell her what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.86,1:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.08,1:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 900 resists, 950 resists, 975 resists, 980
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.08,1:17:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,resists, 990 resists.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.08,1:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.08,1:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 900 resists, 950 resists, 975 resists, 980
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.24,1:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,resists, 990 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.24,1:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,990 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists, 980 resists.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.24,1:18:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 1000 resists.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.24,1:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I didn't tell her what I was holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.44,1:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth makes the body go strong quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.00,1:18:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a very fast response.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.44,1:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you hold something in mind and you press down with two fingers, the person resists
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.58,1:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to the same degree as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.22,1:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.28,1:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're pressing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.50,1:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The reaction is very quick, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.17,1:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't hold a thing in mind and press down,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.55,1:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wait a minute, and then press down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.79,1:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it'll create a doubt in your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.63,1:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you verbalize it, I suggest you do it non-verbally.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.59,1:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you may come back later with a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.63,1:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,well, it's because of what I said, the person heard me, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.39,1:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell them what you're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.06,1:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hold a famous painting in mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.48,1:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say, now, what I'm, let's see,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.82,1:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there was recently a rediscovery of a great painter,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.84,1:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,about a year or two ago, what was that great painting
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.62,1:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that he rediscovered, one of the greatest masters
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.40,1:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of all time, and the argument was
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.80,1:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it was legitimate or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.06,1:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So Van Gogh, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.26,1:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.10,1:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.94,1:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It started with an R, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.64,1:19:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the greatest, like Titian or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.82,1:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the question was whether it was legitimate or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.58,1:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so just for curiosity, yeah, we asked,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.06,1:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is it legitimate or not, and it is, it is, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.82,1:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to think of the name of the artist,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.74,1:19:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the greatest names in art.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.70,1:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Ramiro, I think it was Ramiro.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.84,1:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.26,1:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's worth multi-millions of dollars,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.60,1:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so to be able to tell whether it's false or not false.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.80,1:20:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At home, I have a Picasso that makes you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.26,1:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We hung it in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.11,1:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake Picasso.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.37,1:20:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.07,1:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like a hug, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.23,1:20:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.73,1:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.40,1:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting away easy today, no chowky talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.30,1:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just hug you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.02,1:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So yes, who was that great artist?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.98,1:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.48,1:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.98,1:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the greatest.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.80,1:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a Vermeer?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.80,1:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was Vermeer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.28,1:20:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just ask again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.37,1:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind calibrates over 700, 750, 780.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.95,1:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That Vermeer calibrated around 750.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.06,1:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest art experts have a great deal
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.40,1:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of difficulty deciding whether a piece of art is legitimate
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.80,1:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.30,1:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can tell in a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.53,1:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, from a spiritual perspective
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.01,1:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the long run, does it really
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.23,1:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,matter who wins the upcoming presidential election?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.65,1:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In the long, in the greater context, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.26,1:21:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the greater context, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.58,1:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.02,1:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the unfolding of the collective karma
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.92,1:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind in its expression in the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.68,1:21:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,at this particular time and under these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.85,1:21:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just ask a question myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.19,1:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, the intention of the person I'm holding in mind is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.35,1:21:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of the person I'm holding in mind is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.55,1:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of both.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.77,1:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Both contestants is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.75,1:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They both intend.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.87,1:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They both have integrous intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.73,1:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm worried about a person's intention, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.30,1:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person's intention is integrous,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.98,1:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll lend them my car, if it's not at all, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.85,1:22:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I once lent my car to somebody, and I didn't calibrate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.67,1:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to go get it myself several weeks later.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.85,1:22:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting in his driveway with the key in it out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.32,1:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.00,1:22:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.72,1:22:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Question from the last lecture I went to in this one
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.22,1:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is that in order to raise consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.92,1:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you would embrace the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.08,1:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the best ways to do that
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.88,1:22:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is to pick something that's truly sacred.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.48,1:22:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, beauty, forgiveness, really embrace that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.49,1:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you elaborate a little bit more on that,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.41,1:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and then maybe how you can really get into that in light
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.29,1:22:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of maybe some of our occupations, daily challenges,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.13,1:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,things like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.94,1:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be one with the field, then, is
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.24,1:23:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,like being with the current moment in a generality
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.99,1:23:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than a specificity.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.79,1:23:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, say, the upcoming election.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.05,1:23:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you concerned about?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.25,1:23:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about whether the people are integrous, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.12,1:23:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.32,1:23:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You could then ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.32,1:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is for the highest good of the country?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.74,1:23:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is for the highest good of mankind, et cetera?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.56,1:23:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your alignment with integrity then tends to bring it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.75,1:23:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To see the sacredness of all that exists is a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.51,1:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can will or program.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.95,1:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It reveals itself spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.08,1:24:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're walking through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.68,1:24:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly you see the stunning perfection of one
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.26,1:24:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,thing standing out in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.91,1:24:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You wonder, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.07,1:24:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God revealing the divinity which
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.74,1:24:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is present in all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.53,1:24:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a revelation when you remove the obstacles to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.93,1:24:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the obstacles are dualistic perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.79,1:24:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason we talk about nonlinear reality
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.26,1:24:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it's the fastest pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.36,1:24:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stop and say the flowers are beautiful or not beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.72,1:24:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have to name every flower, I'm really missing what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.18,1:24:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.16,1:24:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're obviously somebody's intention to create beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.72,1:24:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and to uplift the audience, to uplift.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.86,1:25:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever put this together did so in the name of beauty, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.10,1:25:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the intention of the flowers and their arrangement
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.34,1:25:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and their being here is, in a way, worshipful of beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.06,1:25:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of the worship.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.76,1:25:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.30,1:25:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.04,1:25:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to see the beauty of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.21,1:25:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of just becoming aware and sensitive to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.42,1:25:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All things that exist are intrinsically beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.78,1:25:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.28,1:25:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.78,1:25:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So much.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.54,1:25:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk through an alley, and all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.32,1:25:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the alley and everything in it, all the garbage cans,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.48,1:25:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,strike you as an impressionistic painting.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.35,1:25:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.89,1:25:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a stage set.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.23,1:25:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you see something the world calls ugly,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.10,1:25:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,look at it as a stage set.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.17,1:26:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a stage set.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.73,1:26:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk through the alley, there's the tin can,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.35,1:26:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the kitty climbing on the tin can,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.63,1:26:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the little rats scurrying all around.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.11,1:26:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's a perfect stage set.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.59,1:26:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.01,1:26:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The theatrics of the presents itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.32,1:26:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see through our artistic eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.74,1:26:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see the intrinsic beauty of the garbage can.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.16,1:26:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love old garbage cans.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.36,1:26:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they just, whoa, they're so droopy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.16,1:26:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And this little rat runs up the side,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.82,1:26:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you run down the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.20,1:26:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.66,1:26:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Theater, it's like theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.52,1:26:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all of existence like theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.91,1:26:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the politicians getting out there and .
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.33,1:26:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like fantastic theater, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.65,1:26:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that were up a couple of months ago
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.05,1:26:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,shaving their fists.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.10,1:27:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hysterical, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.40,1:27:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All the fish shaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.48,1:27:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate them, 135, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.00,1:27:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.18,1:27:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.92,1:27:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.04,1:27:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something about the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.40,1:27:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,anatta and individual karma, the anatta doctrine of no mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.92,1:27:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that I'm having problems with this
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.32,1:27:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because our language in subject predicate fashion
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.06,1:27:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is naturally dualistic and the semantic difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.68,1:27:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But who actually changes the program in that DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.44,1:27:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that has an end during his life in our life's journey?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.30,1:27:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no actual I that has a substantial essence,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.44,1:27:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,how can we affect our own spiritual advancement?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.16,1:27:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we become?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.72,1:27:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.84,1:27:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has free will?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.22,1:27:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it that no individual I is needed?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.90,1:27:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.16,1:27:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, how does karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.40,1:27:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a composition you're reading me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.82,1:27:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not asking me a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.32,1:28:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just trying to qualify all these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.00,1:28:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you a D on the presentation so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.20,1:28:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, how?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.08,1:28:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want you to cut to the quick of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.44,1:28:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we have individual karma if it happens at 200
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.64,1:28:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have a, you know, an etheric brain?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.16,1:28:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you have a collective karma up to 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.20,1:28:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the animals do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.71,1:28:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you transcend consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.68,1:28:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you, for the first time, come into spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.54,1:28:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.47,1:28:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From that point on, you have an individual consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.52,1:28:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,individual consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.84,1:28:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to that time, you share the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.30,1:28:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You share the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.90,1:28:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See, one forgiving thought can take you right out
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.98,1:28:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of that field, one forgiving thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.68,1:28:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It all takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.38,1:28:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you actually remembered your karma as a tiger?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.88,1:28:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.19,1:29:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The tigerness, I subjectively intuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.91,1:29:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember being a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.35,1:29:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But many lifetimes, you do remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.07,1:29:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And because they were highly significant
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.31,1:29:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from a spiritual viewpoint and beyond a certain level,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.79,1:29:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you consciously remember them in excruciating detail,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.46,1:29:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.66,1:29:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.16,1:29:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember them, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.28,1:29:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If the individual I does not exist as a substantial essence,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.28,1:29:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we not remember a lot of different?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.82,1:29:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting into a lot of languaging now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.70,1:29:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just kind of.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.20,1:29:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.78,1:29:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.54,1:29:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you really asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.23,1:29:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was raised Roman Catholic.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.69,1:29:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I studied philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.91,1:29:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And my problem is the no mind and who reincarnates.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.29,1:29:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.25,1:29:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.17,1:29:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's what I figured.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.89,1:29:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apples and oranges, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.21,1:29:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.03,1:29:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.19,1:29:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.25,1:29:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What reincarnates.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.65,1:29:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What reincarnates.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.13,1:30:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What reincarnates is that which thinks it has a mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.85,1:30:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is nonlinear doesn't reincarnate,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.05,1:30:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because it never incarnated.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.77,1:30:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.27,1:30:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we had more time to answer him thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.98,1:30:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would take longer to decipher and translate it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.36,1:30:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,into language.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.60,1:30:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this one goes to the satellite room
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.98,1:30:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.98,1:30:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to speak to both of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.24,1:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot the satellite room.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.66,1:30:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even remember when I say a lot of the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.52,1:30:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.02,1:30:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.40,1:30:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.90,1:30:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, tell them to come in here and say hello to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.68,1:30:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.48,1:30:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.14,1:30:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.64,1:30:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a facilitator.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.34,1:30:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm naturally grabbing the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.68,1:30:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what the relationship is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.70,1:30:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,between a sudden change in our level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.08,1:30:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of divorces that are happening
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.98,1:30:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or breakup of relationships, specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.98,1:30:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,long-term relationships?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.04,1:30:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I think there's a relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.66,1:31:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,between the collective consciousness level and the level
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.54,1:31:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.00,1:31:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.66,1:31:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Break up of relationships? Is that what you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.91,1:31:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the increase of our conscious level.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.92,1:31:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked the question. I never researched it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.55,1:31:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have anything to do with the indigo children?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.81,1:31:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.60,1:31:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you. May I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.06,1:31:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People may stay together because they're evolved or because they're not evolved.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.24,1:31:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or one or the other, or more evolved than the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.12,1:31:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Too dumb to know about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.74,1:31:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or too smart to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.60,1:31:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.86,1:31:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One, would you take a picture with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.82,1:31:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.78,1:31:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other, something that I would call a discrepancy,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.28,1:32:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure there's an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.76,1:32:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You had two calibrations for Descartes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.38,1:32:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One in Power vs. Force, $4.99.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.86,1:32:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, Descartes is not $4.99.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.52,1:32:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.79,1:32:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes is around $4.60.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.37,1:32:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes is around $4.60, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.86,1:32:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes is around $4.60.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.08,1:32:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes is around $4.60, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.72,1:32:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,$4.60, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.22,1:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Einstein is $4.99.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.62,1:32:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes is, no, Descartes is differentiated between res interna and res externa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.79,1:32:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would be around $4.50, $4.55.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.00,1:32:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.02,1:32:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's two of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.34,1:32:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me shake your hand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.07,1:33:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not tall.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.21,1:33:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a midget that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.69,1:33:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me shorty, so it's not that he's tall, it's that I'm short, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.98,1:33:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.60,1:33:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time to see you, and I just finished Power vs. Force.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.52,1:33:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is on kinesiology for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.88,1:33:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we just keep continuing to practice to be able to really do it as effectively as you're doing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.20,1:33:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't forget we have a lot of practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.24,1:33:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.06,1:33:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell, you can, there's a lot of people you can study with on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.88,1:33:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's people who do kinesiology, teach kinesiology all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.82,1:33:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there are always keeps a list of them, and when we speak around, we often meet teachers of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.48,1:33:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.51,1:33:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's based somewhat on a sensitivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.91,1:34:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, I can ask a question, and she'll already feel the energy of the answer run down her,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.62,1:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,her arm, before the muscles react.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.38,1:34:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten so sensitive that I can experience the energy that is running down her arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.20,1:34:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I already got the answer before her arm does one thing or the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.44,1:34:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've been doing it together for.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.12,1:34:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, if I ask if Descartes over 460, I already feel the positive energy out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.24,1:34:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes are on 460.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.88,1:34:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's clear that this is the basis of knowing the truth to the false for all of those that don't have this, or for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.66,1:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we just continue to practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.02,1:34:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying there are people.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.06,1:34:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anybody that you recommend for teaching?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.60,1:34:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are teachers all over the country and and most chiropractors know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.74,1:34:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Most holistic practitioners of medicine know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.79,1:34:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There are study groups that study this work here all over the country that do it routinely.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.15,1:34:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we just started a study group on this in Denver.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.29,1:34:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're just beginning, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.73,1:35:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're trying to fine tune our skills.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.29,1:35:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.49,1:35:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.09,1:35:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.63,1:35:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Going and doing something like.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.07,1:35:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we intend to do a teaching video on kinesiology, but we're bored with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.93,1:35:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So we never did do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.31,1:35:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if kinesiology is the basis for us to know truth, then we would need to learn it to be able to.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.87,1:35:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way to verify truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.47,1:35:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.01,1:35:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see what's happened to her arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.73,1:35:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to be useful, but she's not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.23,1:35:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.15,1:35:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as I say, it's like writing a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.67,1:35:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know why after the new book comes out, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.73,1:35:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.75,1:35:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.35,1:35:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get where it's at, you've got it, you know, and it's just sort of getting the space of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.99,1:35:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.29,1:35:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're around people that know how to do it or do it all the time, you sort of pick it up intuitively from them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.51,1:35:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.45,1:35:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.82,1:35:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.32,1:35:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And can I have a hug, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.18,1:35:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.04,1:35:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't have a vested interest in the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.87,1:36:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to ask a question in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.73,1:36:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.49,1:36:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the two contestants for the presidency, I'm only interested in whether they have integrity or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.47,1:36:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If one of them makes your arm go weak, then that would not be for the highest good of the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.01,1:36:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with who they are, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.10,1:36:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they all went to Ivy League colleges, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.25,1:36:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.75,1:36:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.25,1:36:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.51,1:36:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, Lily Tomlin's bag lady tests, reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.23,1:36:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing more than a collective hunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.81,1:36:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily Tomlin, I love her, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.51,1:36:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.69,1:36:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to humor is one of the pathways to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.43,1:36:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought it would be too comical to write a book about it, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.12,1:36:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.62,1:36:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because forgiveness, you see, is innate to humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.42,1:37:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you calibrate, we, in fact, for the book we did, we calibrated all the most best-known humorists, the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.40,1:37:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,most recent times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.82,1:37:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all around 480 or so, very erudite.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.78,1:37:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All the best-known humorists calibrate, you know, 460, 475, 480.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.42,1:37:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's something disarming about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.68,1:37:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think humor is one of the best ways of learning and teaching, and one of the best ways to
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.08,1:37:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,experience yourself, because if you take yourself humorously, nobody can get you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.80,1:37:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize you're stupid and ugly, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.15,1:37:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.23,1:37:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What can they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.02,1:37:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is on a personal note.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.40,1:37:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is blocking me from manifesting my full abilities as a manual therapist?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.66,1:37:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As a what?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.66,1:37:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Manual therapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.66,1:37:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a physical therapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.66,1:37:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's blocking your talents?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.66,1:37:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's blocking your talents.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.66,1:38:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think something's blocking your talents?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.16,1:38:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Classes that I take, advanced classwork, I'm often able to manifest picking up restrictions
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.22,1:38:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and doing the techniques, but in my own clinic, I'm lacking.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.22,1:38:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel lacking.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.22,1:38:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.15,1:38:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a personal, investigative matter we'd have to go into, I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.99,1:38:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you may have to do self-confidence or your role, how you picture your role, expectations
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.14,1:38:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of yourself and others.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.14,1:38:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.14,1:38:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a complicated question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.14,1:38:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have to look at it, you know, take five, ten minutes of asking multiple questions to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.24,1:38:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,try and find out what section it's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.12,1:38:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.14,1:38:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.14,1:38:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.14,1:38:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've tried prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.14,1:38:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.14,1:38:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.14,1:38:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.14,1:38:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.14,1:38:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To be an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.68,1:38:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's not what you're blocked about.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.54,1:38:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blocked about what's standing in your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.54,1:39:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you really ask the Holy Spirit is for a miracle of understanding about what
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.70,1:39:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.70,1:39:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.70,1:39:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What you really want is the understanding, the awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.70,1:39:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden you're, and then forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.70,1:39:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're driving down the highway and all of a sudden you're like, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.70,1:39:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.70,1:39:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get to the house and ah, got what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.70,1:39:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.70,1:39:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.22,1:39:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.22,1:39:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of nowhere, like a flying fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.91,1:39:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.91,1:39:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It went someplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.91,1:39:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.46,1:39:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what I was going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.84,1:39:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If Jesus, did Jesus calibrate at a thousand throughout his entire physical lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.84,1:39:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, did he, why was he attacked so viciously?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.84,1:39:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was he what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.84,1:39:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacked.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.84,1:39:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacked so viciously.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.84,1:39:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he calibrated at a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.84,1:39:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't exempt you from what you're here for.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.84,1:39:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He made a commitment, came down from heaven with no previous physical incarnation as a
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.51,1:39:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,human.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.51,1:40:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He served the Lord by giving up physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.54,1:40:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.54,1:40:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So he provided a service to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.69,1:40:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He served the truth, yes, for the sake of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.69,1:40:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,From that level, you think giving up your physical body is a great sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.49,1:40:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.49,1:40:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the violet flame I see when I focus on an object?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.34,1:40:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.34,1:40:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.34,1:40:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The violet flame.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.34,1:40:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet flame.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.34,1:40:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.34,1:40:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that refers to.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.34,1:40:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pentecostal flame you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.34,1:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire, a violet fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.34,1:40:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I focus on things, I see a violet fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.34,1:40:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a healing energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.34,1:40:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.34,1:40:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.34,1:40:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.34,1:40:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have to research it specifically.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.34,1:40:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.91,1:40:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.91,1:40:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just like the last lady said.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.91,1:40:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, everyone has their unique little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.91,1:40:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to kind of,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.58,1:40:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to kind of, you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.58,1:40:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to kind of, you have to ask several questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.11,1:40:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going to have to check it out, you know, individually.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.45,1:41:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.45,1:41:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.45,1:41:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got four minutes, and four people left.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.37,1:41:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.73,1:41:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.79,1:41:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My experience of myself and a lot of other people I know is that at certain times we're
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.63,1:41:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of acting very loving and very forgiving to other people in our relationships.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.45,1:41:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.31,1:41:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,other times we're still capable of having intense anger, rage, and all sorts of negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.31,1:41:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Does any of that have any bearing on one's overall consciousness level?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.31,1:41:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The fluctuating moods and emotions don't change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.57,1:41:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What changes it is the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.57,1:41:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your calibrated level of consciousness and your karma is dependent upon the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.57,1:41:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So your spiritual will may be aligned in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.63,1:41:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got some karmic whatchamacallits coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.63,1:41:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the karmic propensities you have is that of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.63,1:42:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this protoplasmic brain and its machinery.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.63,1:42:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you transcend each of those things and handle each one as the best you can as it unwinds.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.62,1:42:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is like a CD and the story is unwinding.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.62,1:42:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.75,1:42:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you handle each thing as it comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.88,1:42:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Do you have any questions for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.07,1:42:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a joke. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.15,1:42:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was puzzled about something.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.15,1:42:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that my puzzlement shows so badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.63,1:42:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's because I would like to spend half an hour answering each question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.63,1:42:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm always frustrated because there's a lot more that can be said.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.63,1:42:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be brief. I won't be half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.63,1:42:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a question until you started answering questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.63,1:42:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it created one.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.63,1:43:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke of the energy with the weird name.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.53,1:43:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.53,1:43:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I work for an agency that works with difficult to manage children.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.46,1:43:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are the worst of the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.46,1:43:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are sexual predators.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.46,1:43:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had an experience with one of these where he was at a dark place, a low place.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.10,1:43:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And there were a couple of times when I felt him drawing energy from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.06,1:43:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as he came out of that and started to go into the abuse cycle,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.06,1:43:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were worried that he was going to, well, they call it make a bad choice, but offend.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.06,1:43:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a connection with him, which I took to be very negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.70,1:43:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.70,1:44:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was able to feel what he felt as a predator.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.52,1:44:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had been taught that it was like a wolf on the hunt, but it wasn't that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.52,1:44:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pulling from right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.58,1:44:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it scared me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.68,1:44:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it really was very scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.68,1:44:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt very defiled.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.68,1:44:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I had to be cleansed after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.74,1:44:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering now if perhaps it was a backwash of that or a backwash of energy, of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.94,1:44:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.94,1:44:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason Jesus Christ said to avoid evil is for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.51,1:44:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a practice of hanging out and trying to help evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.60,1:44:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.60,1:45:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play with evil?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.73,1:45:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.73,1:45:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.73,1:45:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Jesus Christ said, avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.18,1:45:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you help?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.18,1:45:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Jesus Christ tell you to try and help evil?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.53,1:45:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he teach?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.91,1:45:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to avoid evil because you're not equipped to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.00,1:45:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why it scared me so?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.00,1:45:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.00,1:45:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.00,1:45:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want a recitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.00,1:45:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.00,1:45:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Exorcists themselves are hit by those kind of energies.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.60,1:45:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the risk you take when you work with people of that particular level.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.60,1:45:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're extremely well guarded, extremely well guarded, it will sense a vulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.60,1:45:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,whichever chakra it might be, because you don't know your karmic inheritance from past lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.60,1:45:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what you did to others and what you still owe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.60,1:45:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really playing with fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.30,1:45:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.30,1:45:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.30,1:45:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.30,1:46:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.30,1:46:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.30,1:46:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived this far.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.30,1:46:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.30,1:46:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, just one last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.30,1:46:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.30,1:46:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.30,1:46:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.30,1:46:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.30,1:46:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.30,1:46:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.30,1:46:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to sound so tough with people.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.30,1:46:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But occasionally you have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.30,1:46:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.30,1:46:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.30,1:46:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because otherwise people will be in walking around in circles.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.30,1:46:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.30,1:46:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.30,1:46:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.30,1:46:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.42,1:46:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.42,1:46:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.42,1:46:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.42,1:46:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.00,1:46:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.00,1:46:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.00,1:46:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.00,1:46:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.00,1:46:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.74,1:46:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.74,1:46:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Loolooland, Lala Land.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.74,1:46:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, are we done now?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.74,1:46:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.14,1:46:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.14,1:46:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.14,1:46:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking up to your walking question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.14,1:46:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.75,1:46:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, who are the great Masters on the planet right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.75,1:46:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrate between seven hundred and one thousand?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.52,1:46:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're karmically blessed or equipped,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.19,1:47:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on to them and they yeah and you run into the experience of such a being see that comes about
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.51,1:47:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through karmic inheritance and you can't name them oh you don't want to name them they get enough
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.32,1:47:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,mail as it is if you love them you know you would keep them anonymous i keep them anonymous
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.27,1:47:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,i don't have a request to hug you but if you will stand i would like to greet you in the indian way
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.45,1:47:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we acknowledge our teachers by treating their
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.51,1:47:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,personage as sacred so if you will strand may i what should i do she wants to stand up
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.59,1:47:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,stand up oh thank you very much god bless you i realized the divinity i realized that's the
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.25,1:47:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sacredness and the ancientness of this gesture thank you all right so i thank you all for your
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.68,1:48:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,presence i give thanks for that for i am
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.48,1:48:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.98,1:48:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,i am truly blessed by your presence amen
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.58,1:48:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,oh god
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.69,1:48:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah my pen where they oh that's not a pen that's a pointer
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.65,1:48:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i have such a collections of pointers and i keep leaving them in my baggage my luggage and
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.63,1:48:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere what good do they do me when they're home
